## Operator review checklist before send

- [ ] Invoice number and amount verified against Project Tracker xlsx
- [ ] Reminder count `{{N}}` matches actual count of prior reminders (search Sent items)
- [ ] Days-overdue calculation correct ({{TODAY}} - invoice_due_date)
- [ ] Customer AR contact email is current (not stale from a year ago)
- [ ] Ashley CC'd
- [ ] No threatening language (collections-agency tone is for legal, not Maaz)
- [ ] No mention of 4% interest charge unless customer is at #5+ AND operator says to include
- [ ] Length 60–100 words

