## Variant: AIMS-routed AR

For Aramco / ADNOC / KNPC / SATORP / etc. where AIMS invoices the client and SRE invoices AIMS:

- **To**: AIMS finance contact (Fazal or Junaid, depending on which one handles that customer)
- **CC**: Ashley
- Subject: `AIMS: SRE Invoice {{INVOICE_NUMBER}} - Reminder #{{N}}`
- Body: chase AIMS for the SRE-to-AIMS payment, not the AIMS-to-client payment
